commit message:
Filter out pull requests from issue list.

As the issue list API doesn't support that filtering, also use the issue
search API for listing issues.
Also allow editing PR from PR fragment, as there is no obvious way to
access the issue for a PR now.

Closes #324
Subtract PR count from issue count in repo overview.
Fix loading indicator being hidden prematurely.
Make pull request count loading more efficient.

Fix NPE.

Happened when entering issue search mode without being logged in.
Update to latest AS and support libraries.
Work around NPEs in SVG parser.

Treat .ts as TypeScript, not MPEG2TS.

Closes #332.
